<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>150</hymn_number>
<key>A</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Galilee ah Bawipa Jesuh, Cawnpiak pah in, A umkal tawn, Vancung kong
 cawnpiaknak caah, Tahchunhnak kha a hman tawn hna.

[C1]
   Maw, Galilee ram thluachuakmi Jesuh a chung ah a leng tawn, Kan ram
   zong nih Jesuh a herh, A chungah leng ve seh kan ti.

[V2]
 Pangpar phunkip tlimno vialte, Lei le van thil, Vialte hna nih,
 Pathian thatnak a sunparning, A thiannak he an kan chimh fawn.

[C2]
   Maw, Galilee ram thluachuakmi Jesuh a chung ah a leng tawn, Kan ram
   zong nih Jesuh a herh, A chungah leng ve seh kan ti.

[V3]
 Fiang tein hmu kho u si law, Vawlei dihlak, Biakinn a si, Sermi thil
 vialte hna zong hi, Pathian lamkal tu an si dih.

[C3]
   Maw, Galilee ram thluachuakmi Jesuh a chung ah a leng tawn, Kan ram
   zong nih Jesuh a herh, A chungah leng ve seh kan ti.</lyrics>
<title>GALILEE PHILHLONAK CH150</title>
</song>